Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《良医》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously on "The Good Doctor".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:04.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-嘿 停车  -丹尼\N{\rYUANWEN}- Hey! Stop! - Danny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:08.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,答应我一件事\N{\rYUANWEN}Just promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:10.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-什么  -不要给我用阿片类药物\N{\rYUANWEN}What? No opioids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他让你不要用\N{\rYUANWEN}He asked you not to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他因为痛苦出现了心动过速\N{\rYUANWEN}He's tachycardic and hypertensive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有高血压 他会休克的\N{\rYUANWEN}because of the pain. He's going into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-他不会 他在恳求你  -他快死了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's not. He's praying. He's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:18.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,原谅我\N{\rYUANWEN}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:21.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要和家人回到德州去\N{\rYUANWEN}I need to go back to Texas with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,昨天的开颅手术你犯了个错\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun: You made an error in yesterday's craniotomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你缝合的时候只用了八针\N{\rYUANWEN}You closed with only eight sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可那种尺寸的伤口应该缝十针\N{\rYUANWEN}The size of the wound required 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:28.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要弄清楚原因\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to figure out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:29.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我中风了\N{\rYUANWEN}I've had a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 微中风\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes. A small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,格拉斯曼医生 请告诉我们下一步该怎么做\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Glassman, please tell us what the next step is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁叫一下保安 肖恩 你越界了\N{\rYUANWEN}Glassman: Somebody please call security. Shaun, you are out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,回答\N{\rYUANWEN}Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:39.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rYUANWEN}It's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在我的手术室里 在我的同事面前\N{\rYUANWEN}You humiliated me in public in my operating room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:44.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当众羞辱了我\N{\rYUANWEN}in front of my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:45.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道这对我伤害有多大吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you have any idea how much that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么做\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:49.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可以别再烦我了\N{\rYUANWEN}You can just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不认为你应该辞职\N{\rYUANWEN}Park: I don't think you should resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:52.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为你不需要独自抚养孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Because you don't have to do it all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:54.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是我每天早上愿意醒来的理由\N{\rYUANWEN}You're the reason I wake up in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:56.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以不管未来会发生什么\N{\rYUANWEN}so whatever there is to figure out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我唯一想要的就是我们能一家人一起面对\N{\rYUANWEN}all I want in the world is for us to do it as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:01.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想作为朋友给你个提醒\N{\rYUANWEN}I wanted to give you a heads- up as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:02.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我决定辞职了\N{\rYUANWEN}I've decided to resign.
