Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要一起来吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Wanna join?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不了谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,爸爸墨菲 欢迎回归\N{\rYUANWEN}Papa Murphy, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫的照片\N{\rYUANWEN}Pictures of Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我正要问呢\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just about to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这样 我就不用不停掏手机了\N{\rYUANWEN}This way, I avoid the disruption of pulling out my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:21.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看看这笑容啊 跟他妈一个样\N{\rYUANWEN}Look at that smile! Just like his mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那张他正在拉臭 这张是 准备拉臭\N{\rYUANWEN}He was pooping in that one. Here he is about to poop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拉臭主题系列\N{\rYUANWEN}A theme develops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的眼睛跟你一样哎 肖恩\N{\rYUANWEN}He's got your eyes, Shaun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得去找下林医生\N{\rYUANWEN}I need to find Dr. Lim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:35.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们留着吧 我给所有人都备了一份\N{\rYUANWEN}You may keep those. I made enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马库斯从西班牙发来问候\N{\rYUANWEN}Marcus sends greetings from Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还以为他去越南禅修呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, I thought he was at a meditation retreat in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,本来是 现在他正在走圣地亚哥之路\N{\rYUANWEN}He was, and now he's walking the Camino de Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他就开心了\N{\rYUANWEN}How nice for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我少了俩外科医师 却没人肯批准再请一个新人\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm two surgeons down with no one to approve hiring a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要董事会任命一名临时主席 立刻马上\N{\rYUANWEN}I need the Board to appoint an Interim President, stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望不是奥布莱恩\N{\rYUANWEN}Just as long as it's not O'Brien.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\rYUANWEN}They wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从一位负责董事会会议的工作人员那里听说\N{\rYUANWEN}I heard from a staffer who covers Board Meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的名字在候选人名单上\N{\rYUANWEN}that his name's on the short list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:01.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是最不适合这个职位的候选人\N{\rYUANWEN}Ugh. Of the worst possible candidates for the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:03.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早上好 史蒂夫的照片\N{\rYUANWEN}Good morning! Pictures of Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不用拄拐了\N{\rYUANWEN}You no longer have your cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 PT说我好了 很高兴见到你回来\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah. PT said I was ready. I'm glad to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想加入你正在跟的病例\N{\rYUANWEN}I would like to join your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他真可爱 墨菲医生 欢迎回归\N{\rYUANWEN}He's adorable, Dr. Murphy. Welcome back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,肖恩 我很高兴见到你\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun, I'm thrilled to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我不确定作为一个新手父亲来说\N{\rYUANWEN}but I'm not sure this is the case where you want
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个病例适不适合你\N{\rYUANWEN}to start as a new dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是个令人激动且有挑战性的手术\N{\rYUANWEN}It is an exciting and challenging surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们这么短时间内就能过来\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you for coming in on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们好 我是肖恩·墨菲医生\N{\rYUANWEN}Hello. I am Dr. Shaun Murphy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,主治医师 也是个男宝的父亲\N{\rYUANWEN}attending surgeon and father of a baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:39.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他两周大 而今天是我第一天回来上班\N{\rYUANWEN}He is two weeks old, and today is my first day back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这不会影响我作为你们儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}but that will not affect my performance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,医生的专业水准\N{\rYUANWEN}as your son's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有适合杰克的心脏这是真的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is it true there might be a heart for Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:48.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 但是心脏暂时还没准备好\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, but the heart isn't available yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:51.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且准备好后我们也韦必能拿到\N{\rYUANWEN}and we may not get it once it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们以前也经历过这种情况\N{\rYUANWEN}We've been through this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心脏暂时还没准备好是什么意思\N{\rYUANWEN}Why isn't the heart available yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,捐赠者家人还需要点时间\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, the donor family is still saying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,进行告别 然后才会关闭生命维持系统\N{\rYUANWEN}their goodbyes before they turn off life support.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:08.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰克跟捐赠者心脏完全匹配\N{\rYUANWEN}Jack is an excellent match for the donor heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的最新回声显示\N{\rYUANWEN}and his latest echo indicates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的心肌病和整体心脏功能\N{\rYUANWEN}that his cardiomyopathy and overall cardiac function
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:14.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都变差了 所以他应该排在名单的最前面\N{\rYUANWEN}has worsened, so he should be at the top of the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是想多做几项测试\N{\rYUANWEN}I just want to run some additional tests
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确保他其它方面都很健康\N{\rYUANWEN}to make sure he's otherwise healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这有个问题\N{\rYUANWEN}There is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里有一小块划伤 应该是他指甲挠的\N{\rYUANWEN}There is a small scratch, likely from his fingernails,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已经发展成蜂窝组织炎和脓肿\N{\rYUANWEN}which has developed cellulitis and an abscess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果感染扩散并发烧\N{\rYUANWEN}If the infection spreads and he spikes a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰克就不能接受移植手术了\N{\rYUANWEN}Jack will be ineligible for the transplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们必须马上解决这个问题\N{\rYUANWEN}We have to lance and debride it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早\N{\rYUANWEN}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:52.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是史蒂夫 我们的儿子 现在已经两周大了\N{\rYUANWEN}This is Steve, our son, who is now two weeks old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:55.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫 这就是住在走廊尽头的那个坏脾气男人\N{\rYUANWEN}Steve, this is the grumpy man who lives down the hall
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你最爱的小毯子就是他送的\N{\rYUANWEN}and gave you your favorite blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你能猜中他的名字 肖恩深感意外\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun was very impressed you guessed his first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要试试猜下中间名吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Wanna take a stab at the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:06.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,艾伦\N{\rYUANWEN}Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我一直想要叫他鲍伊\N{\rYUANWEN}I was lobbying pretty hard for Bowie,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,既然起名为什么不用\N{\rYUANWEN}because why not name your kid after
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:11.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,史上最酷的人名呢\N{\rYUANWEN}the coolest person who every lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是肖恩很坚持\N{\rYUANWEN}But...Shaun insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有时间应该过来看看他\N{\rYUANWEN}You should come over sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们俩可以一起发出哼唧声然后做鬼脸\N{\rYUANWEN}You two both grunt a lot and make strange faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:24.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我最近事情很多 所以\N{\rYUANWEN}I've got a lot going on, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们就住隔壁 你根本就没什么事\N{\rYUANWEN}We live next door. You have nothing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:30.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你只是生气 我明白\N{\rYUANWEN}You're mad. And I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:34.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你真的打算无视肖恩 史蒂夫和我到永远吗\N{\rYUANWEN}But are you really gonna ignore Shaun and Steve and me forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是这么打算的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没有无视你\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not ignoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且他也很好看\N{\rYUANWEN}And he's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恭喜了\N{\rYUANWEN}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我试过了\N{\rYUANWEN}I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,吃奶的时候有发绀症状吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Any cyanosis while eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:01.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,昨晚她的嘴唇是有那么一丝丝发蓝\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe a hint of bluishness on her lips last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我什么都没注意到\N{\rYUANWEN}I haven't noticed anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但考虑到她之前的手术和特纳综合征\N{\rYUANWEN}But given her prior surgery and the Turner syndrome,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们还是\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought we should
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,血流量变少了\N{\rYUANWEN}The blood flow is reduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看起来伊伊登的主动脉狭窄\N{\rYUANWEN}It looks like Eden's aortic stenosis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:18.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,发展得比我们预期的要快\N{\rYUANWEN}has progressed more rapidly than we were expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们能给她服用β受体阻滞剂吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can we put her on beta blockers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:25.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可以试试 但是鉴于瓣膜发育不良\N{\rYUANWEN}We can try, but given how dysplastic the valve is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得这样用处不大\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't think it will do much good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可能想多做几项医学成像 但是\N{\rYUANWEN}You'll want to get more imaging, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为伊伊登可能很快就需要再做一次手术了\N{\rYUANWEN}Ithink Eden's gonna need another surgery- - very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:49.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心脏核磁证实瓣膜严重狭窄\N{\rYUANWEN}Cardiac MRI confirmed severe narrowing of the valve,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,梗阻和左心室功能障碍\N{\rYUANWEN}obstruction, and Ieft ventricular dysfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊伊登需要一个新的主动脉瓣\N{\rYUANWEN}Eden needs a new aortic valve,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,否则她的心脏衰竭会越来越严重\N{\rYUANWEN}or her heart failure will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想用机械的还是冷冻活性同种带瓣主动脉\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you thinking mechanical or cryopreserved homograft
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来代替\N{\rYUANWEN}for the replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,新生儿的机械瓣膜需要建造\N{\rYUANWEN}Mechanical valve for a neonate needs to be built,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,未来需要手术\N{\rYUANWEN}and it will require future surgeries
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还要终身服用抗凝血药\N{\rYUANWEN}plus lifetime blood thinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,冷冻保存的瓣膜有退化的风险\N{\rYUANWEN}Cryopreserved valves risk degeneration down the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这是一个可靠的办法\N{\rYUANWEN}but it is a solid idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尤其是作为主动脉瓣置换手术的一部分\N{\rYUANWEN}especially as part of the Ross Procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能的并发症呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Possible complications?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,主动脉瓣功能不全 肺动脉狭窄\N{\rYUANWEN}Aortic insufficiency, pulmonary stenosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要点时间 来讨论一下各种方宰\N{\rYUANWEN}We can take some time, discuss the different options-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,做主动脉瓣置换手术\N{\rYUANWEN}Do the Ross Procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我让亚设给她做准备\N{\rYUANWEN}I'lI have Asher get her prepped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是时候进场了吧\N{\rYUANWEN}It's time to get off the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not sure what you're referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是打算扔球给我吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you gonna throw me a ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你之前也管理过医院\N{\rYUANWEN}You've run the hospital before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再坚持几个月没有问题\N{\rYUANWEN}You can handle a few more months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是可以 但我为什么要这么做呢\N{\rYUANWEN}I can, but why would I want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-所以你是拒绝咯  -对\N{\rYUANWEN}That's a no? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就准备好迎接临时院长奥布莱恩吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Get ready for O'Brien.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\rYUANWEN}They would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就像是毛与巴塞尔·弗尔蒂碰面一样不可能\N{\rYUANWEN}That's like Mao meets Basil Fawlty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是晦涩且过时的比喻了\N{\rYUANWEN}Wow. That's two obscure and dated references.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们绝对不会让奥布莱恩上的\N{\rYUANWEN}They're never gonna move on O'Brien.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很明显 他在董事会的候选名单上\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, apparently, he's on the Board's short list.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要你下场 他压根没有机会\N{\rYUANWEN}Throw your hat in the ring, he won't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:14.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还是老实呆着吧 不过我会处理好的\N{\rYUANWEN}My hat's gonna stay on my head, but I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的 杰克\N{\rYUANWEN}Jordan: Okay, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:20.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道自己耳朵后面有个小肿块吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You know that little bump behind your ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:22.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得用锋利的东西戳一戳\N{\rYUANWEN}We have to poke it with something sharp,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,虽然会很痛 但这是必须的\N{\rYUANWEN}which will hurt, but we have to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望你能得到一颗新的心脏\N{\rYUANWEN}so hopefully you can get a new heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:32.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱抱熊先生来陪你咯\N{\rYUANWEN}But Mr. Snugglepuff is here to keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,亚设说墨西哥卷外卖车的菜单上加了西班牙辣香肠\N{\rYUANWEN}Asher said the taco truck added chorizo to the menu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吃到爆\N{\rYUANWEN}and it's bussin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:43.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找个晚上 我们应该一起点份餐吧\N{\rYUANWEN}The next late night, we should share an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是我的菜 谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Not really my thing. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确证了是片状丘疹\N{\rYUANWEN}The sheet papoose is secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:49.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 卡鲁医生 把孩子抱起来\N{\rYUANWEN}Good. Dr. Kalu, cradle the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:52.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,艾伦医生 请给耳朵后部消毒\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Allen, sterilize the area behind the ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 宝贝 别看\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay, baby, don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:09.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的眼睛还没法聚集到8到12英寸\N{\rYUANWEN}His eyes are not yet able to focus beyond 8to 12 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,脓肿很深\N{\rYUANWEN}Kalu: The abscess is pretty deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能需要一段时间才能痊愈\N{\rYUANWEN}It may take a while to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伤口吸液器怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}What about a wound vac?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:26.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们没有那么小的\N{\rYUANWEN}We don't have one small enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:28.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rYUANWEN}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,蛆虫\N{\rYUANWEN}Maggots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,直接用抗生素不是更好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}How are those better than just using antibiotics?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,蛆虫清理坏死组织的速度更快\N{\rYUANWEN}Maggots work faster to clear necrotic debris
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它们的唾液和其他消化分泌物\N{\rYUANWEN}on account of the antimicrobial nature
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有抗菌的特性\N{\rYUANWEN}of their saliva and other digestive secretions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把那些虫子放在我宝宝身上安全吗\N{\rYUANWEN}It's safe to put those bugs on my baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-幼虫而已  -这些是医用蛆虫\N{\rYUANWEN}Larvae. - These are medical maggots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已经经过了特别消毒\N{\rYUANWEN}They've been specially disinfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,绝对安全\N{\rYUANWEN}It's completely safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下 就算是我儿子史蒂夫 我也会用蛆虫\N{\rYUANWEN}I would use maggots on my son, Steve, in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,虽然不太可能有这种情况\N{\rYUANWEN}That is unlikely to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我举这样的例子是为了让你放松\N{\rYUANWEN}but I hope the parallel puts you at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就干吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想喝点咖啡吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在办公室还有一些蛋白质棒\N{\rYUANWEN}Or I have a stash of protein bars in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你想吃点什么 去就好了\N{\rYUANWEN}But if you want something, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:33.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的家人为什么来这里\N{\rYUANWEN}What's your family here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:36.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心脏移植 希望是给我们的儿子杰克的\N{\rYUANWEN}A heart transplant, hopefully, for our son, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他多大了\N{\rYUANWEN}How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,12周\N{\rYUANWEN}12 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的女儿伊登11周大了\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh. My daughter, Eden, is 11 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她现在正在做心脏手术\N{\rYUANWEN}She's having heart surgery right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会为你们祈祷的\N{\rYUANWEN}Y'all will be in my prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:53.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是杰克的第一次手甫吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is this Jack's first surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他还做过其他手术\N{\rYUANWEN}He's had other procedures,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这次是他第一次做心脏直视手术\N{\rYUANWEN}but this would be his first open heart surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还不一定呢\N{\rYUANWEN}If it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果能做上 我建议术后使用比萘芬乳膏\N{\rYUANWEN}When it happens, I recommend Biafine cream for post- op.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它含有一种叫做三乙醇胺的天然化合物\N{\rYUANWEN}It contains a natural compound called trolamine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对伊登的恢复很有帮助\N{\rYUANWEN}It really helped with Eden's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你女儿做了几次手术\N{\rYUANWEN}How many surgeries has your daughter had?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一次 七周的时候做的\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, one. At seven weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:19.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊登和我都是老手了\N{\rYUANWEN}Eden and I are old hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:23.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们都是非常坚强的女士\N{\rYUANWEN}You're two very resilient ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是凯特·皮尔斯 这是我丈夫欧文\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm Kate Pierce. This is my husband, Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是摩根雷·茨尼克\N{\rYUANWEN}Morgan Reznick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是亚历克斯·帕克\N{\rYUANWEN}Alex Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你能不能\N{\rYUANWEN}Would you like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可以的 来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah! You can do itl Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:55.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就对了 你成功了\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh! There you go! You got it! You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你成功了\N{\rYUANWEN}You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗨 爸爸 重回工作岗位感觉怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}Hi, Daddy. How is it being back at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:03.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我刚在一个比史蒂夫大几个月的婴儿身上放了蛆\N{\rYUANWEN}I just applied maggots to a baby a few months older than Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是史蒂夫吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that Steve?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他应该去睡觉了\N{\rYUANWEN}He is supposed to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的俯卧训练做得不错\N{\rYUANWEN}Mm. He's doing well with tummy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你昨天说他有点落后进度\N{\rYUANWEN}And you mentioned yesterday he was behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我想应该再加几分钟\N{\rYUANWEN}so Ithought I'd add a few extra minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\rYUANWEN}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,俯卧训练不应该占用他的睡眠时间\N{\rYUANWEN}Tummy time should not be extended into his sleep window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没有收到应用提醒吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you not get the app alert?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他7分钟前就有应该睡觉了\N{\rYUANWEN}You are seven minutes into nap time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:26.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有收到 我可能错过了\N{\rYUANWEN}Nope. I guess I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,睡眠时间不足会使他过度疲劳\N{\rYUANWEN}Delaying his nap could make him overtired
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也可能影响他下一次进食\N{\rYUANWEN}or delay his next feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,时间安排很重要\N{\rYUANWEN}The schedule is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道了 肖恩 只是几分钟而已\N{\rYUANWEN}I know, Shaun, I know. It's just a few extra minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:39.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,八分钟了 这可不算少 都好久了\N{\rYUANWEN}Eight minutes. That is not a few. It is several.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我该让史蒂夫躺下来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, I should go put Steve down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rYUANWEN}Bye- bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们不得不中止手术\N{\rYUANWEN}We had to abort the procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊登其中一个双尖肺动脉瓣\N{\rYUANWEN}Eden has a bicuspid pulmonary valve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:59.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,与主动脉之间的组织连接太少了\N{\rYUANWEN}There wasn't enough tissue to attach it to the aorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们还观察到瓣膜有泄露\N{\rYUANWEN}And we observed leaking at the valve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她心脏衰竭的速度比我们想象的还要快\N{\rYUANWEN}Her heart is failing even faster than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们下一步怎么办\N{\rYUANWEN}What's our next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,蛆虫起作用了\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh. The maggots worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰克宝宝的感染已经清除\N{\rYUANWEN}Baby Jack's infection has cleared,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心脏已经在来的路上了\N{\rYUANWEN}and the heart is on its way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊登有两个瓣膜有病变\N{\rYUANWEN}Eden has two bad valves
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:26.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并且心力衰竭在快速恶化\N{\rYUANWEN}and rapidly progressing heart failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:30.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只有一颗供移植的心脏 但有两个婴儿都需要\N{\rYUANWEN}We have one donor heart and two babies who need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们来决定哪个宝宝能得到这颗心脏\N{\rYUANWEN}It's up to us to decide which baby gets this heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰克已经等了三个月了\N{\rYUANWEN}Jack has been waiting for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,移植手术是他唯一的选择\N{\rYUANWEN}A transplant is his only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他可以用心室辅助器 直到找到合适的心脏\N{\rYUANWEN}He could go on a VA. D. until another heart is available.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那可能需要几个月的时间\N{\rYUANWEN}Kalu: That could take months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心室辅助器不适合杰克 因为\N{\rYUANWEN}And a V. A. D. isn't a good option for Jack because of the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,摩根 摩根\N{\rYUANWEN}Morgan. Morgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:52.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不能进来 你们两个都不行\N{\rYUANWEN}You can't be here. Neither of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我哪也不去\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't be anywhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要么你找人给我打镇静剂 要么\N{\rYUANWEN}so either someone should sedate me or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也不是不行\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that can be arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我和帕克待在这并不是什么问题\N{\rYUANWEN}It's only a problem that Park and I are here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除非干扰了你们的决定 你们自己做决定就好\N{\rYUANWEN}if we influence your decision, so don't let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我什么也不会说的\N{\rYUANWEN}I won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡鲁医生\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Kalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,至于杰克的心室辅助器 他体重过轻\N{\rYUANWEN}as far as the V. A. D. for Jack, he's underweight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以并发症的风险很高\N{\rYUANWEN}so a high risk of complications,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还可能感染 出血 中风\N{\rYUANWEN}infections, bleeding, stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:27.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这对伊登来说也不是一个好办法\N{\rYUANWEN}It's not a great option for Eden, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:31.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们等机械替代瓣膜的时候 伊登可以\N{\rYUANWEN}Eden can go on ECMO while we're waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先用体外膜肺氧合\N{\rYUANWEN}for mechanical replacement valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,体外膜肺氧合是有风险的 尤其是对患有特纳综合征的婴儿\N{\rYUANWEN}ECMO has risks, especially for a baby with Turner syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,持续的时间越长 并发重症的\N{\rYUANWEN}And the longer she's on it, the greater the risk
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,风险就越大\N{\rYUANWEN}of serious complications.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能等不及瓣膜来了\N{\rYUANWEN}The valves may not get here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不说两句吗 墨菲医生\N{\rYUANWEN}Care to weigh in, Dr. Murphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:55.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,基于体型和血型 杰克和伊登\N{\rYUANWEN}Jack and Eden are equally good matches to the donor heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,与捐赠的心脏都配型成功了\N{\rYUANWEN}based on size and blood type.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有别的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,直说吧 肖恩\N{\rYUANWEN}It's okay, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有了这颗心\N{\rYUANWEN}Without this heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰克就会天折\N{\rYUANWEN}Jack will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊登没有这颗心 也可能死亡\N{\rYUANWEN}Eden may also die without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但她还有别的选择\N{\rYUANWEN}But she has other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,虽然有风险的 但仍然有选择\N{\rYUANWEN}They are risky, but they are options.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那颗心应该给杰克\N{\rYUANWEN}Jack should get the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,今晚我们就给伊登做体外膜肺氧合\N{\rYUANWEN}We'll put Eden on ECMO tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会联系艾伯特\N{\rYUANWEN}And Ill contact Abbott
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尽快拿到1毫米瓣膜\N{\rYUANWEN}about getting the 15- millimeter valves ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:05.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 很抱歉 我们今晚改约好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey. I'm sorry. Can we rain- check tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我累坏了 杰罗姆答应过\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm exhausted, and Jerome promised
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们一起看一部精彩的犯罪电影\N{\rYUANWEN}that we could watch a nice crime procedural.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:13.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有时候忙了一周需要好好放松\N{\rYUANWEN}Sometimes you need a case of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的\N{\rYUANWEN}Mmm! My favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一份切达牛腩加淡酱\N{\rYUANWEN}One cheddar brisket with mild sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:27.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这样小史蒂夫下次吃饭才不尝不出辣味\N{\rYUANWEN}so little Steve's next meal doesn't burn his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:31.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你真是救苦救难 我饿死了\N{\rYUANWEN}You are a treasure. I am starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可怜的伊登 不得不做体外膜肺氧合了\N{\rYUANWEN}Poor Eden, having to go on ECMO.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:39.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有可怜的摩根和帕克\N{\rYUANWEN}And poor Morgan and Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已经耗一天了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's...been a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:45.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,佩雷斯不在 你还好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And how are you holding up? Without Perez?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:53.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在家里或工作中发生的每件事\N{\rYUANWEN}Everything that happens, at home or at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:55.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我都想第一个告诉他\N{\rYUANWEN}he's the first person I want to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而我不能\N{\rYUANWEN}And I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或者我不应该\N{\rYUANWEN}Or I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:03.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的很想念他\N{\rYUANWEN}I really miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:05.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可以都告诉我啊\N{\rYUANWEN}You can tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果太过专业 我可能听不懂\N{\rYUANWEN}If it's too surgical, I may not understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:11.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我会频频点头 表现出感兴趣的样子\N{\rYUANWEN}but I am excellent at nodding and acting interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:16.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会一直在你身边 亚设也是\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm here for you. So is Asher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:21.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了 跟我说嘛\N{\rYUANWEN}What's going on? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但婴儿不会去传八卦\N{\rYUANWEN}Babies are terrible at gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,亚设和我本来约今晚出去玩的\N{\rYUANWEN}Asher and I were supposed to hang out tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就我们两个人\N{\rYUANWEN}just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你得去看看他吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you need to check on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 如果他看到我 那就不肯撒手了\N{\rYUANWEN}No. If he smells me, I'll never get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他会平静下来的\N{\rYUANWEN}He'll settle back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:36.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你和亚设计划\N{\rYUANWEN}So you and Asher had plans
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:38.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他放我鸽子 为了杰罗姆\N{\rYUANWEN}He blew me off for Jerome- -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:41.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为他为了伊登劳心劳力了一天 这我理解\N{\rYUANWEN}because he had a hard day on Eden's case, which I get,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:42.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我今天也很辛苦\N{\rYUANWEN}but I had a hard day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫真闹了\N{\rYUANWEN}Steve's not settling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不着急 你今天很辛苦吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, he can wait a minute. You had a hard day, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:52.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好像每个人都有需要自己的人 除了\N{\rYUANWEN}It- - It just seems like everybody has someone except- -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:59.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我马上就回来\N{\rYUANWEN}I am so sorry. I- I will be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我发誓\N{\rYUANWEN}I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:19.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你本可以不用这么做的 肖恩\N{\rYUANWEN}You didn't have to do this, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:22.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我比这医院里的任何人都更严谨\N{\rYUANWEN}I am more thorough than anyone else in this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:27.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,体外膜肺氧合开始\N{\rYUANWEN}Starting ECMO.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:48.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我刚收到董事会成员盖尔的一封电子邮件\N{\rYUANWEN}Lim: I just got an e- mail from Gail on the Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:52.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我怎么突然成了临时主席的头号候选人\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm suddenly a top candidate for Interim President?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:53.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\rYUANWEN}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想要那个位子\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want that job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:59.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,试试看呗 你总比奥布莱恩强\N{\rYUANWEN}It's bet better you than O'Brien.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:00.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是个好经理\N{\rYUANWEN}You're a good manager, you're- -
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:02.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你很受人尊重\N{\rYUANWEN}you're well- respected,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:04.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且 你是个多元化的女性\N{\rYUANWEN}and, you know, as a diverse woman
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:06.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,人性不是多元化的\N{\rYUANWEN}People aren't diverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:07.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是属于一个未被充分看见的群体\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm part of an underrepresented group.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:09.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就去做一个完美的候选人\N{\rYUANWEN}Right. That. Makes you an ideal candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:12.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看 盖尔喜欢这个主意\N{\rYUANWEN}Look. Gail loved the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:14.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我恨你  -不客气\N{\rYUANWEN}I hate you. You re welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 史蒂夫\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun: I am glad to see you, Steve,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:26.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你应该睡着的\N{\rYUANWEN}but you are not supposed to be awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:28.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在他午睡的时候打了个瞌睡\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, I- I fell asleep during his afternoon nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们直到4:30才醒来\N{\rYUANWEN}We didn't wake up until 4: 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:33.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你得设个闹钟 时间安排很重要\N{\rYUANWEN}You need to set an alarm. The schedule is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:35.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:41.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明天我要在一个12周大的婴儿\N{\rYUANWEN}Tomorrow I am doing a heart transplant
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,身上做心脏移植手术\N{\rYUANWEN}on a 12- week- old baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:45.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 你需要睡眠\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay. You need sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:47.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,的确如此\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:51.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去睡觉吧 今晚我来应付史蒂夫\N{\rYUANWEN}Go to bed. I'll handle Steve tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么吵我怎么睡\N{\rYUANWEN}I- I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.23,0:23:55.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没事的 那你的降噪耳机呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Shh, it's okay. What about your noise- canceling headphones?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:58.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我习惯侧身入睡 我戴耳机没法睡\N{\rYUANWEN}I fall asleep on my side. I cannot do that in those.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:00.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不如你去格拉斯曼家过夜\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe you could go spend the night at Glassman's?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:02.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rYUANWEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.61,0:24:05.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的办公室呢 你能睡在那里吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What about your office? Can you sleep there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:26.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心肌病 心力衰竭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.80,0:24:27.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心肌病 心力衰竭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.47,0:24:28.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心肌病 心力衰竭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.44,0:24:45.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,诊断\N主动脉瓣狭窄 特纳综合征
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:54.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可以用一颗心救两个宝宝\N{\rYUANWEN}We can save them both with one heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.96,0:25:04.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这叫做多米诺骨牌移植 杰克的心脏正在衰竭\N{\rYUANWEN}It's called a Domino Transplant. Jack's heart is failing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.63,0:25:06.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但他的瓣膜是健康的\N{\rYUANWEN}but his valves are healthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:07.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以在杰克接受心脏移植后\N{\rYUANWEN}so when Jack receives the donor heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.63,0:25:10.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将用他的瓣膜替换伊登受损的瓣膜\N{\rYUANWEN}we will use his valves to replace Eden's damaged ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.22,0:25:11.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个鲜活的同型移植供体意味着伊登不需要进行\N{\rYUANWEN}A fresh homograft donor means Eden won't need
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.89,0:25:14.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,多次手术或血液稀释剂\N{\rYUANWEN}multiple surgeries or blood thinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.22,0:25:16.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一颗心可以救两个孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}One heart could save both babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.23,0:25:18.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,瓣膜衰竭的几率有多大\N{\rYUANWEN}What are the chances of valve failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.44,0:25:20.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很小的 杰克的瓣膜功能很好\N{\rYUANWEN}Minimal. Jack's valves are very functional
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.61,0:25:22.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尽管他有心肌病\N{\rYUANWEN}despite his cardiomyopathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.77,0:25:24.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,成功的几率很高\N{\rYUANWEN}The odds of success are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.61,0:25:29.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我们最好的选择 对伊登来说\N{\rYUANWEN}It's the best option we have- for Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.53,0:25:31.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那杰克呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And for Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.45,0:25:34.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在取出他的心脏时 我们必须非常小心\N{\rYUANWEN}We would have to be very careful while removing his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.33,0:25:36.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以免损坏他的瓣膜\N{\rYUANWEN}so as not to damage his valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:38.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就意味着需要花更多的时间做分流术上\N{\rYUANWEN}That would mean more time on bypass,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.46,0:25:41.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这意味着出血或感染的风险更大\N{\rYUANWEN}which means a greater risk of bleeding or infection
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.88,0:25:43.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是个很难开口的要求\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a lot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.42,0:25:45.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们有拒绝的权力\N{\rYUANWEN}They can always say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.84,0:25:48.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What would you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.98,0:26:03.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你已经24小时没吃东西了\N{\rYUANWEN}You haven't eaten anything in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.73,0:26:04.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:09.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不管他们怎么决定 我们都会挺过去的\N{\rYUANWEN}No matter what they decide, we'll get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.57,0:26:10.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.74,0:26:12.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么 别让你宽心吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What, try to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.28,0:26:15.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 没错 没什么意义 也很烦人\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, exactly. It's pointless and annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.37,0:26:20.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道你还没把伊登也视作我的女儿\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, I get that you don't think of Eden as mine yet
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.08,0:26:21.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你在她做任何医疗决定时\N{\rYUANWEN}and that's why you haven't included me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.92,0:26:23.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都没让我参与\N{\rYUANWEN}in any of her medical decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.88,0:26:26.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是说我需要那个\N{\rYUANWEN}Not that I need that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.13,0:26:27.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或者说我不同意你的任何选择\N{\rYUANWEN}or disagree with any of your choices- -
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.59,0:26:29.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你这样惹我生气又是为了分散我的注意力吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is pissing me off another attempt to distract me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.30,0:26:31.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不是想找茬\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not trying to pick a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.26,0:26:33.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是想让你知道 我爱那个女孩\N{\rYUANWEN}I just want you to know that I love that girl
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:36.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对她视为己出 而且\N{\rYUANWEN}like she's my own, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.68,0:26:38.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我和你一样害怕\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm as scared as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.72,0:26:42.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你能让我帮你 因为\N{\rYUANWEN}And I wish you'd let me help you because...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.85,0:26:44.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可以同舟共济\N{\rYUANWEN}we're in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.48,0:26:45.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,仅此而已\N{\rYUANWEN}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.65,0:26:49.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的不想看到你晕过去\N{\rYUANWEN}And I really don't want you to pass out,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.36,0:26:51.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以请吃点东西 或者至少喝点什么\N{\rYUANWEN}so please eat or drink something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.50,0:27:04.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我们的孩子能救你孩子的命 我们不胜荣幸\N{\rYUANWEN}If our baby can save your baby's life, we'd be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.01,0:27:17.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会永远爱你\N{\rYUANWEN}"I'll love you forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.14,0:27:19.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会永远喜欢你\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll like you for always.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.39,0:27:23.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要我还活着 你就是我的宝贝\N{\rYUANWEN}As long as I'm living, my baby you'll be. "
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:31.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天啊 真是催人泪下\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, my God. What a tear- jerker.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.65,0:27:36.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得找一本爸爸的医学杂志看\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to find one of Daddy's medical journals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.12,0:27:37.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,提醒\N{\rYUANWEN}Reminder- -
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.33,0:27:39.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,五分钟后小睡\N{\rYUANWEN}nap time in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.37,0:27:48.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么取消音箱婴儿应用程序的同步播报啊\N{\rYUANWEN}How do I un- sync the baby app from our speaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.42,0:27:51.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 不 你不应该取消\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, no. You should not do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.51,0:27:54.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我设置这个是为了让你记住日程安排\N{\rYUANWEN}I set it up so you can remember the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.13,0:27:56.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当白天只有我和史蒂夫在家的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}When it's just me and Steve home during the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.89,0:27:58.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我喜欢更\N{\rYUANWEN}I like to be a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.97,0:28:01.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,灵活一点 随机应变\N{\rYUANWEN}flexible, go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.14,0:28:02.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 我把插头拔掉好了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll just I'll just unplug it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.93,0:28:06.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它有内置电池 以防停电\N{\rYUANWEN}It has a battery in case of power outages.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.81,0:28:09.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莉亚 当我工作的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}Lea, when I'm at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.86,0:28:12.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我喜欢知道你和史蒂夫在做什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I like knowing what you and Steve are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.49,0:28:17.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这会让我觉得我仍然是他生活的一部分\N{\rYUANWEN}It makes me feel like I am still a part of his day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.57,0:28:19.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果史蒂夫不用作息时间表休息的话\N{\rYUANWEN}And when Steve gets off his sleep schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.28,0:28:20.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就得去医院睡觉了\N{\rYUANWEN}I have to go sleep at the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.87,0:28:23.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就会更想你们俩了\N{\rYUANWEN}and I miss you both even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.45,0:28:26.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 我们也想你 你睡得怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}Aw, we missed you, too. How did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.62,0:28:29.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不很好 但我想到了一个很好的办法\N{\rYUANWEN}Not well. But I came up with a very good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.04,0:28:30.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来救两个孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}to save both babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.42,0:28:32.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得去准备手术了 我爱你\N{\rYUANWEN}I have to go prep for my surgery now. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:35.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林医生 我们有个会议要讨论\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Lim, we have a meeting to review- -
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.34,0:28:36.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等一下 肖恩\N{\rYUANWEN}One minute, Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.93,0:28:39.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,盖尔 当然 多样性和代表性\N{\rYUANWEN}Gail, of course, diversity and representation
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.18,0:28:41.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也应该考虑在内 但鉴于这是\N{\rYUANWEN}should be considered, but given this is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.47,0:28:43.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个临时职位 我认为最重要的是\N{\rYUANWEN}an interim position, I think the top priority is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.81,0:28:46.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找到一个从第一天起就能立刻开始工作的人\N{\rYUANWEN}finding someone who can hit the ground running from day one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.89,0:28:48.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我们要找有过相关工作经验的人\N{\rYUANWEN}And that means someone who's done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.90,0:28:50.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他太谦虚了 不会自吹自擂\N{\rYUANWEN}He's too modest to sing his own praises,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.73,0:28:52.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我认为他是最合适的人选\N{\rYUANWEN}but I think he's the obvious choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.69,0:28:55.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,非常令人信服的论点 谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Hmm. Compelling argument. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.16,0:29:01.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,老年人也是一个代表性不足的群体\N{\rYUANWEN}And seniors are also an underrepresented group.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.78,0:29:05.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲医生和我将在一号手术室从杰克开始\N{\rYUANWEN}Lim: Dr. Murphy and I will start with Jack in OR 1
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.29,0:29:08.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,亚设 你在隔壁和伊登一起帮她准备\N{\rYUANWEN}Asher, you'll be with Eden next door getting her ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.29,0:29:10.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,艾伦和卡鲁 你们俩将接受捐赠的心脏\N{\rYUANWEN}Allen and Kalu you two will receive the donor heart
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.38,0:29:11.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并为移植做准备\N{\rYUANWEN}and prep it for transplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.96,0:29:15.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后我和林医生会给杰克做分流术\N{\rYUANWEN}Then Dr. Lim and I will put Jack on bypass
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.34,0:29:17.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并把他核心体温降温到25度\N{\rYUANWEN}and start cooling him to 25 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.30,0:29:19.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,考虑到他的年龄和潜在的健康状况\N{\rYUANWEN}Given his age and underlying medical condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.22,0:29:23.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的分流术时间不应该超过两个小时\N{\rYUANWEN}he should not be on bypass for longer than two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.18,0:29:25.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,植入杰克的新心脏大约需要90分钟\N{\rYUANWEN}Putting in Jack s new heart will take about 90 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.85,0:29:28.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这样我们就有半个小时的时间来移除旧的那个\N{\rYUANWEN}That leaves us half an hour to remove the old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.90,0:29:30.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,肖恩在移植新心脏的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}While Shaun is transplanting the new heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.98,0:29:33.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我来切除杰克的瓣膜\N{\rYUANWEN}I will be excising Jack's valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.48,0:29:35.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们没有一丁点犯错的余地\N{\rYUANWEN}We have zero room for error.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.32,0:29:38.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让你们的病人做好术前准备\N{\rYUANWEN}Prep your patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.99,0:29:45.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真是人兴奋的病例\N{\rYUANWEN}Jordan: Exciting case.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.25,0:29:51.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要同时救两个孩子 你就说个对\N{\rYUANWEN}We're saving two babies at once, and your commentary is"yep"?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.34,0:29:56.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是在同意你的看法 尽量少说话\N{\rYUANWEN}I was agreeing with you. With as few words as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.13,0:29:58.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你过去两周一直在少说话\N{\rYUANWEN}which you've been doing for the last two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.93,0:30:03.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你对我有意见 就直说\N{\rYUANWEN}If you have a problem with me, just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.52,0:30:07.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay. Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.56,0:30:10.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对你和你处理佩雷斯那个病例的方式有意见\N{\rYUANWEN}I have a problem with you and how you handled Perez's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.69,0:30:12.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-那是真的蠢  -是你让我直说的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's completely stupid. You just said I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.69,0:30:14.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我又没说你说了我就会同意你的看法\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't say I would agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.19,0:30:16.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你无视病人的意愿\N{\rYUANWEN}You overrode our patient's wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.11,0:30:17.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-佩雷斯因此离开了  -佩雷斯因此活了下来\N{\rYUANWEN}and Perez is gone because of it. Perez is alive because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.94,0:30:20.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不知道如果你听了他的话会发生什么\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't know what would have happened if you'd listened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.99,0:30:22.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你做了你认为最好的决定\N{\rYUANWEN}You made the decision you thought was best.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.91,0:30:24.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不管别人想要的是什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Didn't matter what anyone else wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.66,0:30:26.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 但你无权这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry, but you don't get to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.45,0:30:28.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,却不承担相应的后果\N{\rYUANWEN}and not deal with the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.41,0:30:30.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么相应的后果\N{\rYUANWEN}The consequences?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.58,0:30:32.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我失去了一个我很在乎的人\N{\rYUANWEN}I lost someone I care about a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.83,0:30:35.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我每天都在想他\N{\rYUANWEN}and I miss him every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.96,0:30:39.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的很努力地在把注意力集中在我生活中的美好事物上\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm really trying hard to focus on the good things in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.09,0:30:40.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我热爱的工作\N{\rYUANWEN}the job I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.93,0:30:43.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以为我拥有的朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}the friends I thought I had
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.97,0:30:49.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但感觉每个人都在向前看 留我孤身一人\N{\rYUANWEN}But it feels like everyone is moving on, and I'm just alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.02,0:30:55.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你可以不用担心怎么惩罚我了\N{\rYUANWEN}Spare yourself the burden of punishing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.16,0:31:04.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把她术前准备做好 盖好 然后麻醉\N{\rYUANWEN}Lim: Get her prepped, draped, and under anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.45,0:31:06.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望30分钟后见\N{\rYUANWEN}I'lI see you in 30 minutes, hopefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.30,0:31:22.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有一套备用的\N{\rYUANWEN}I had an extra set.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.01,0:31:26.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不必是天主教徒\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't have to be Catholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.14,0:31:28.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这只是为了提醒你 你并不孤单\N{\rYUANWEN}They can just be a reminder that you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.98,0:31:32.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.12,0:31:58.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有很多疤痕组织需要剖开\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun: There is a lot of scar tissue to dissect through.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.67,0:32:00.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,心肌病导致杰克的心脏增大\N{\rYUANWEN}The cardiomyopathy has caused Jack's heart to enlarge
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.84,0:32:03.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并粘连在胸壁上\N{\rYUANWEN}and adhere to his chest wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.97,0:32:06.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为了保住瓣膜\N{\rYUANWEN}This will take longer than planned
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.05,0:32:08.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要花费比计划更长的时间\N{\rYUANWEN}in order to preserve the valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.30,0:32:09.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们检查了二尖瓣\N{\rYUANWEN}Kalu: We inspected the mitral valve.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.68,0:32:11.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,房间隔完好无损 心脏看起来不错\N{\rYUANWEN}The atrial septum is intact. The heart looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.85,0:32:13.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,艾伦医生 连接肺静脉\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Allen, connect the pulmonary veins
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.48,0:32:15.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,准备左心房套囊\N{\rYUANWEN}to prep the left atrial cuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.10,0:32:16.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡鲁医生 你和我们一起\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Kalu, you're with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.40,0:32:22.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 增加流量 冷却至25度\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay. Increase flows and cool to 25 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.11,0:32:23.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,开始计时\N{\rYUANWEN}Start the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.82,0:32:30.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加油 小花生\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on, Peanut.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.12,0:32:32.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们随机应变了 但现在是午睡时间\N{\rYUANWEN}We went with the flow, but now it's nap time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.58,0:32:35.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 安稳点\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on. Settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.00,0:32:44.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们差一点就成功了 小花生\N{\rYUANWEN}Ohh! We were so close, Peanut.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.34,0:32:46.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要切开主动脉\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun: I need to transect the aorta,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.09,0:32:48.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是主动脉和瓣膜相连的地方有很厚的粘连\N{\rYUANWEN}but there are thick adhesions where it meets the valve.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.76,0:32:51.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你现在只有1小时14分钟来植入新心脏\N{\rYUANWEN}You now only have an hour and 14 minutes to put the new heart in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.39,0:32:54.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,环就在我解剖刀尖\N{\rYUANWEN}The annulus is at the tip of my dissection.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.52,0:32:57.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我划伤它 主动脉瓣就没用了\N{\rYUANWEN}If I nick that, the aortic valve is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.40,0:32:59.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,前缩 我们没时间了\N{\rYUANWEN}Anterior retraction. We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.94,0:33:01.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰克的移植手术有很大风险\N{\rYUANWEN}Jack's transplant is at serious risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.52,0:33:02.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,梅斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Metz.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.98,0:33:05.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墨菲医生 你得中止手术\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Murphy, you need to abort this procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.44,0:33:07.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,肖恩 伊登仍然可以选择体外膜肺\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun, ECMO is still an option for Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.99,0:33:09.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你需要中止  -搞定了\N{\rYUANWEN}You need to abort- - Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.71,0:33:16.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,瓣膜完好\N{\rYUANWEN}The valves are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.71,0:33:21.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,准备好接受捐献的心脏了\N{\rYUANWEN}Ready for the donor heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.26,0:33:28.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-她怎么样了  -准备好了\N{\rYUANWEN}- How is she? - Ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.89,0:33:30.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,生命体征很好\N{\rYUANWEN}Nurse Hawks: Vitals are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.76,0:33:32.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打开她的胸腔 在我恢复瓣膜的同时\N{\rYUANWEN}Open her chest and start her on bypass
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.22,0:33:33.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给她做分流术\N{\rYUANWEN}while I recover the valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.72,0:33:36.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,手术刀 瓣膜看起来怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}Ashen Scalpel. How do the valves look?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.48,0:33:38.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比我们在成像上测到的要大一点\N{\rYUANWEN}A little bigger than we measured on imaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.44,0:33:40.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这使得吻合很困难\N{\rYUANWEN}Makes the anastomosis challenging.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.90,0:33:43.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是能正常工作吧\N{\rYUANWEN}But it can still work?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.19,0:33:44.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,必须能\N{\rYUANWEN}It has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.83,0:33:57.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,五分钟后开始喂孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Feeding time starting in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.17,0:34:05.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,位置不太好\N{\rYUANWEN}Lim: It's not seating perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.21,0:34:06.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让我们试试荷包缝合\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's try a purse string suture.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.80,0:34:08.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,7-0血管缝合线\N{\rYUANWEN}Asher: 7-0 Prolene.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.35,0:34:18.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,搞定 生理盐水\N{\rYUANWEN}Got it. Saline.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.86,0:34:25.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,主动脉瓣旁有泄漏\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a paravalvular leak at the aortic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.86,0:34:28.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要不换个缝合线\N{\rYUANWEN}How about pledgeted sutures?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.32,0:34:31.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么小的婴儿 这可能会导致血管狭窄\N{\rYUANWEN}In an infant this small, that could cause stenosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.41,0:34:32.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们再试一次\N{\rYUANWEN}We try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.08,0:34:35.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,7-0血管缝合线\N{\rYUANWEN}7-0 Prolene.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.50,0:34:39.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已经差不多两个半小时了\N{\rYUANWEN}Jordan: It's been almost two and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.04,0:34:40.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得让他断开体外循环\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to get him off bypass.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.37,0:34:42.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,主动脉吻合完全\N{\rYUANWEN}The aortic anastomosis is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.08,0:34:45.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,松开主动脉 开始恢复体温\N{\rYUANWEN}Unclamp the aorta and start rewarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.50,0:34:47.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\rYUANWEN}Kalu: Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.34,0:34:53.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等 祈祷他的心脏能开始跳动\N{\rYUANWEN}We wait...and hope his heart starts beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.78,0:35:10.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都快三个小时了 你觉得是出什么事儿了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}It's been almost three hours. Do you think something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.33,0:35:25.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,缝合线撑住了\N{\rYUANWEN}Asher: The sutures are holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.33,0:35:28.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在这个小东西只需要跳起来\N{\rYUANWEN}Lim: Now the little thing just has to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.25,0:35:30.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,开始给她升温 减少流量\N{\rYUANWEN}Start warming her up. Decrease the flows.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.93,0:35:43.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要电击\N{\rYUANWEN}Shaun: We need to shock him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.61,0:35:48.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,离手\N{\rYUANWEN}Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.03,0:35:56.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\rYUANWEN}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.46,0:36:13.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,手术很成功\N{\rYUANWEN}The surgeries were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.34,0:36:15.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你俩的孩子都很好\N{\rYUANWEN}Both your babies are doing very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.13,0:36:17.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们很快就能见到他们了\N{\rYUANWEN}and you can see them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.43,0:36:19.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.10,0:36:24.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.89,0:36:26.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你救了我们的女儿\N{\rYUANWEN}You saved our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.90,0:36:32.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\rYUANWEN}You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.86,0:36:35.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想我的孩子了 我现在要回家了\N{\rYUANWEN}I miss my baby. I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.70,0:36:45.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 我先去洗个澡\N{\rYUANWEN}Alright. Let me just jump in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.62,0:36:47.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后我们就走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}And then I'm good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.50,0:36:49.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,回家找你男人去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go home to your man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.59,0:36:51.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rYUANWEN}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.34,0:36:53.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 明天好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Bless you. Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.90,0:37:17.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是对的 这个辣香肠真是\N{\rYUANWEN}You're right. This chorizo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:19.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说它什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What'd you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.32,0:37:21.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吃到爆\N{\rYUANWEN}Bussin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.53,0:37:24.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对 绝对好吃到爆\N{\rYUANWEN}Right. Definitely bussin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.38,0:37:31.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想我们可以一起吃\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought we could share an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.31,0:37:46.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉我你没忘拿辣酱\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me you didn't forget the hot sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.36,0:37:59.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rYUANWEN}Hello. Hm
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.07,0:38:01.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫为什么醒着\N{\rYUANWEN}Why is Steve awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.87,0:38:04.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你看起来很糟糕\N{\rYUANWEN}You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.04,0:38:08.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你了\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.00,0:38:10.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫吃过饭 打过嗝 换过尿片\N{\rYUANWEN}Steve has been fed, burped, changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.63,0:38:14.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后被音箱提醒从偶然的小睡中唤醒\N{\rYUANWEN}and woken from his haphazard nap by a speaker reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.63,0:38:18.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊登怎么样了\N{\rYUANWEN}How's Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.63,0:38:21.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好 杰克的移植手术很成功\N{\rYUANWEN}Very good. And Jack's transplant was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.76,0:38:26.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为人父母是很难的\N{\rYUANWEN}Parenting can be very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.89,0:38:30.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是啊 我发现了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah. I've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.60,0:38:34.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,关于什么效果最好\N{\rYUANWEN}There are many hard choices
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.27,0:38:38.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有很多艰难的选择\N{\rYUANWEN}about what works best.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.19,0:38:39.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家有不一样的需求\N{\rYUANWEN}People want different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.16,0:38:44.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会尽量\N{\rYUANWEN}I will try to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.91,0:38:49.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给你多留点空间\N{\rYUANWEN}...make room for your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.87,0:38:53.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,日程安排很重要\N{\rYUANWEN}The schedule is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.38,0:38:55.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我会取消应用程序和音箱同步\N{\rYUANWEN}but I will un- sync the app from the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.13,0:38:59.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我把它丢在外面的消防通道上了\N{\rYUANWEN}I put it out on the fire escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.97,0:39:02.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.76,0:39:04.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的很感激\N{\rYUANWEN}I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.68,0:39:10.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我现在唯一需要的空间是卧室\N{\rYUANWEN}But the only room I need right now is the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.89,0:39:14.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 晚安\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.56,0:39:16.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要借你的降噪耳机一用\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm borrowing your noise- canceling headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.73,0:39:18.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我爱你们俩\N{\rYUANWEN}I love you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.79,0:39:38.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑吗 你推荐了我\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you kidding me? You recommended me? !
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.38,0:39:40.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是在以你为榜样\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just following your example.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.13,0:39:41.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 你就是天生的领导者\N{\rYUANWEN}See? You're a natural leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.76,0:39:44.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我老了 我累坏了 而且我老了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm old. I'm worn out and I'm old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.30,0:39:46.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你这叫明智  -我还记得用转盘电话的日子\N{\rYUANWEN}You're wise. I remember rotary phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.72,0:39:48.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你很重要 你有经验\N{\rYUANWEN}You're vital. You're experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.64,0:39:50.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是医院里最受尊敬的医生\N{\rYUANWEN}You're the most respected doctor in this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.93,0:39:53.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,亚伦 你有专业知识还有\N{\rYUANWEN}Aaron, you have institutional knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.48,0:39:55.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一种天生的 无法解释的庄重\N{\rYUANWEN}and a- - and a natural, unexplainable gravitas.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.77,0:39:58.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你能不能别犯傻了 赶紧接受这份工作\N{\rYUANWEN}Will you please stop being an idiot and just take the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.32,0:40:00.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要再这么自私和固执\N{\rYUANWEN}Stop being selfish and stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.11,0:40:01.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我怎么自私了 我\N{\rYUANWEN}How am I being selfish? Im-
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.53,0:40:03.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们都在呢 那我就省得多找一站了\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, you're together. That saves me a stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.41,0:40:07.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们的推荐使委员会面临\N{\rYUANWEN}Your recommendations presented the Board
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.70,0:40:09.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个非常困难的选择\N{\rYUANWEN}with a very difficult choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.12,0:40:11.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我们没有\N{\rYUANWEN}So we didn't-
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.62,0:40:13.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,选\N{\rYUANWEN}choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.41,0:40:16.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们俩现在是圣博纳文蒂尔医院的\N{\rYUANWEN}You two are the new Interim Co- Presidents
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.00,0:40:17.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,新临时联合院长\N{\rYUANWEN}of St. Bonaventure Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.67,0:40:22.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\rYUANWEN}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.18,0:40:32.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,日程表不是这样的 史蒂夫\N{\rYUANWEN}This is not the schedule, Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.10,0:40:34.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈妈需要睡觉 爸爸需要睡觉\N{\rYUANWEN}Mommy needs to sleep. Daddy needs to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.77,0:40:36.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你需要睡觉\N{\rYUANWEN}You need to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.61,0:40:39.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.65,0:40:42.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,求你了 我们都很累\N{\rYUANWEN}Please. We are both very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.99,0:40:47.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,求你了 我们都很累\N{\rYUANWEN}Please. We are both very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.00,0:40:59.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.54,0:41:03.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不能进去哄 因为莉亚需要睡觉\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't go inside because Lea needs to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.38,0:41:06.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以前总能把他哄睡\N{\rYUANWEN}I've always been able to get him down before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.76,0:41:10.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有时候婴儿就是需要哭一哭\N{\rYUANWEN}Sometimes babies just need to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.81,0:41:21.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}why don't I take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.15,0:41:22.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你去睡一觉\N{\rYUANWEN}Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.65,0:41:28.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没关系 好好休息一下\N{\rYUANWEN}It's okay. Just get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.91,0:41:33.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就小睡一会儿\N{\rYUANWEN}I will just take a short nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.54,0:41:38.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想休息多久就休息多久\N{\rYUANWEN}Take as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.84,0:41:45.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有我呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.26,0:41:55.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有我呢 有我呢\N{\rYUANWEN}I got you. Huh. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.06,0:42:05.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是爷爷\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.07,0:42:06.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你不知道我是谁的话\N{\rYUANWEN}in case you were wondering.
